examples.en: My wife never worked.
I've worked my ass off.
The wine worked.
The plan worked out.
It worked up to right now.
examples.ru: Это работало вплоть до настоящего момента.

examples.en: The plan worked perfectly.
Details are yet to be worked out.
The wood is easily worked.
He worked until he dropped.
examples.ru: Он работал до тех пор, пока не упал /до упаду/.

examples.en: He worked for a small circus.
Each man worked like a demon.
His face worked with emotion.
Her eyes worked their way up.
The plan worked like a dream.
The day shift worked overtime.
He worked on an interim basis.
He worked them nearly to death.
examples.ru: Он заставлял их работать до полного изнеможения.

examples.en: She worked herself into a rage.
I worked to a man called Duncan.
examples.ru: Я работал на человека по имени Дункан.

examples.en: His fingers worked with tension.
They worked hard and so did she.
examples.ru: Они много работали, и она тоже.

examples.en: I worked my butt off in college.
examples.ru: В колледже я работал, как вол.

examples.en: He worked for a brokerage house.
He worked indoors all afternoon.
examples.ru: Весь день он проработал в помещении.

examples.en: She has worked hard all her life.
examples.ru: Она всю свою жизнь упорно работала.

examples.en: He worked outdoors all afternoon.
examples.ru: Он работал весь день на открытом воздухе.

examples.en: We worked from sunrise to sunset.
examples.ru: Мы работали от рассвета до заката солнца.

examples.en: They worked from morning to night.
examples.ru: Они работали с утра до ночи.

examples.en: Everyone worked till they dropped.
We worked together on the project.
examples.ru: Мы вместе работали над этим проектом.
